        parent - The parent of this type.
        mappedName - The name of the node that a schema is attached to. For top level schemas this is the name of the type.

        public static OASArrayTypeImpl.Builder builder(OASType parent,
                                               String mappedName,
                                               String schemaType,
                                               com.reprezen.kaizen.oasparser.model3.Schema schema,
                                               com.reprezen.jsonoverlay.Reference reference,
                                               Map<com.reprezen.kaizen.oasparser.model3.Schema,OASType> visitedTypes)
        Create a new builder for an OASArrayTypeImpl object.
        Parameters:
        parent - The parent of this type.
        mappedName - The name of the node that a schema is attached to. For top level schemas this is the name of the type.
        schemaType - The resolved schema type name.
        schema - The Schema that will be used to build the OASArrayTypeImpl.
        reference - A Reference associated with the schema which may be null.
        visitedTypes - A Map that tracks the visited schemas and the types that were created. This is used to guard against infinite recursion.
        Returns:
        The OASArrayTypeImpl.Builder object.
